---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Disclaimer • Secura Security Suite">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-[#050507] text-neutral-200 selection:bg-cyan-500 selection:text-black flex flex-col justify-between">
    <Header />

    <div class="flex-1 relative">
      <!-- Grid Background overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(6,182,212,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(6,182,212,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:32px_32px] opacity-40 pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/3 w-[450px] h-[450px] bg-cyan-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

      <!-- Content Container -->
      <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-24 z-10">
        
        <!-- Header back button -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <a 
            href="/" 
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors uppercase tracking-wider group"
          >
            <span class="transform group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform inline-block">&larr;</span>
            <span>Back to Home</span>
          </a>
        </div>

      <!-- Hero Header -->
      <div class="border-b border-neutral-900 pb-10 mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-cyan-950/40 border border-cyan-500/30 text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-cyan-400 mb-6 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(6,182,212,0.1)]">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-400"></span>
          <span>LEGAL STANDARDS & EXCLUSIONS</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-white mb-6 font-mono">
          DISCLAIMER
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xs font-mono text-neutral-500">
          Effective: July 17, 2026 &bull; Version 1.0.0
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Disclaimer content -->
      <div class="space-y-10 text-sm text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed font-sans max-w-3xl">
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-md font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">1. No Legal, Financial, or Tax Advice</h2>
          <p>
            All budget tools, expense tracking calculators, currency estimates, and invoice generation PDFs created on the Secura Platform are strictly for general operational support and utility purposes. Secura does not act as a licensed accounting firm, certified public accountant (CPA), or tax attorney.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-400">
            You are urged to consult with a professional tax advisor or licensed lawyer before submitting finalized accounting logs or tax receipts compiled through our client-side modules to government tax authorities.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-md font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">2. Accuracy and Completeness of Calculations</h2>
          <p>
            While our developer invoice builders and budget goal track systems compute values dynamically, errors in rounding, browser float point precision, and external currency conversions may occur. You remain fully accountable for manually double-checking calculated sums, local sales taxes, and invoice aggregates before requesting client payments.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-md font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">3. Password Health and Security Ratings</h2>
          <p>
            The Password Manager includes local strength indicator algorithms (e.g. assessing password length, complexity, character entropy). These ratings are strictly educational and advisory. Achieving a "STRONG" security indicator score does not guarantee absolute immunity against highly specialized phishing schemes, physical device subversions, social engineering, or browser session-jacking attacks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-md font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">4. Platform Uptime and Data Synchronization</h2>
          <p>
            Secura employs redundant cloud databases (Firebase Firestore) to sync your encrypted records globally. However, synchronization speeds and data availability are subject to local internet connectivity, firewall filters, and cloud container network routing. We make no guarantee of uninterrupted, 100% real-time syncing under conditions of local network failure.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Footer stamp -->
      <div class="border-t border-neutral-900 mt-16 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-neutral-600">SECURA COMPLIANCE DIVISION &bull; RISK MANAGEMENT TEAM</span>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-neutral-500">AUDIT CODE: SEC-DISC-01</span>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
    
  <Footer />
</div>
</Layout>
